title: Best Motivational Speech Compilation - DEDICATION
itunes:title: Best Motivational Speech Compilation - DEDICATION
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
DEDICATION! While no road is ever straight and no journey ever easy, dedication and persistence will always lead you to your dreams. Anything worth having takes hard work, discipline and dedication.Featuring one of the best inspirational speeches ever from Marcus Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity), Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity), Eddie Truck Gordon (https://bit.ly/EddieTruckGordonMotiversity), Nathan Harmon (https://bit.ly/NathanHarmonMotiversity), Mat Wilson (https://bit.ly/MattWilsonMotiversity), and more.


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), and Paul Elhart (http://bit.ly/2SiEaIN).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
